<item>
            <title>[QPIDJMS-169] SASL Plain Mechanism should be enforcing UTF-8 encoding</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-169</link>
                <project id="12314524" key="QPIDJMS">Qpid JMS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When encoding the user / pass in the SASL plain mechanism we aren&apos;t enforcing UTF-8 encoding which is the required encoding.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12956225">QPIDJMS-169</key>
            <summary>SASL Plain Mechanism should be enforcing UTF-8 encoding</summary>
